import React from 'react';
import {Card, CardContent, Grid, TextField} from '@material-ui/core'

export const Refugeeform = () => {
  return (
    <Card>
        <CardContent>
            <Grid container spacing={1}>
                <Grid xs={12} sm={6} item>
                    <TextField
                      label="First Name"
                      placeholder="First Name"
                      variant='outlined'
                      fullWidth
                      required
                    ></TextField>
                </Grid>
                <Grid xs={12} sm={6} item>
                    <TextField
                      label="Last Name"
                      placeholder="Last Name"
                      variant='outlined'
                      fullWidth
                      required
                    ></TextField>
                </Grid>
                <Grid xs={12} item>
                    <TextField
                      label="Email"
                      placeholder="Email"
                      variant='outlined'
                      fullWidth
                      required
                    ></TextField>
                </Grid>

            </Grid>

        </CardContent>
    </Card>
  )
}
